reviewText: Person I bought it for Loves it. Good work "Jerry Jerry".
I brought Volume 1 and two and did not care for them. I like the old-school ones with everybody sitting on the stage. The element of surprise. When the show first began it shocked America and me.
Definetly am a jerry springer fan and love his shows if your a fan its a must have set ppv show awsome.....it rocks.

This could be super.  For me though, there will never be a day in my lifetime from birth to the grave that I want to see any woman over 300 pounds in the buff.  Really could have done without that.  I was hoping for an uncensored romp of common folk, and got a trip to the freakin' zoo.  There are some really great gals too, but when you find a cockroach at the bottom of a milkshake, good luck keeping the milkshake down.  I'm a big fan of the TV Show, a fan of Jerry Springer and Steve Wilko, and get a big kick out of the show most of the time.  This DVD though definitely was not quite what I expected.  Adult but really a little bit too silly, even for Jerry Springer.
if you like jerry springer with everyone in the nude this is the video for you.
